Name: SCUOS
About the game: SCUOS is a puzzle game where you need to reproduce patterns from one board on another. How many levels can you pass? There are three board sizes: 4x4, 5x5, 6x6. Each board has own leaders table with high scores. Features: Brain-training gameplay Challenging levels Minimalistic design Leaderboards Contact e-mail: contact@palenogames.ru
